 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/idkhow-part-ways-with-drummer-after-a-series-of-broken-trusts-3500336">Weekes 就证实 iDKHOW 与鼓手分道扬镳，并完成了新专辑的制作工作。</a></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/idkhow-share-funky-new-dance-track-gloomtown-brats-3555478">iDKHOW 分享的时髦新舞曲“Gloomtown Brats”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
